[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0864","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1014","title":"Sun Solaris mail 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 操作系统的 /usr/bin/mail 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户向 mail 命令的 -m 参数传递超长字符串时，程序未对输入长度进行正确边界检查，导致栈缓冲区溢出。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞精心构造恶意载荷覆盖栈中返回地址，从而以 mail 命令的权限（通常为 root 或 mail 组权限）执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.7 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统账号方能利用，无需网络远程访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1014"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.477","remediation":"安装 Sun 当时发布的补丁 106827-01（SPARC）/ 106828-01（x86），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。对于仍运行 Solaris 7 的遗留系统，可移除 /usr/bin/mail 的 setuid root 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/mail）作为临时缓解，但会影响普通用户使用 mail 命令。现代系统建议迁移至受支持的 Solaris 11 或替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93727925026476&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93846422810162&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/672","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3297","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19529","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1014","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0864.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0759","title":"FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 POP邮件服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 的 POP 邮件服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 POP 服务端口发送超长的 USER 或 PASS 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标服务崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 及可能更早的版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前已存在公开的利用代码，攻击者无需认证即可利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0759"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.867","remediation":"建议立即升级 FuseWare FuseMail 至最新可用版本（厂商已停止支持，建议迁移至其他受支持的邮件服务器软件，如 Postfix、Exim）。如无法升级，可在防火墙上限制对 POP 服务（TCP 110 端口）的访问来源 IP，仅允许受信任的内网客户端连接，同时在邮件服务器上配置 fail2ban 等工具对连续认证失败行为进行自动封禁。如 POP 服务非必需，建议直接禁用该服务以减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.crosswinds.net/~fuseware/faq.html#8","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/634","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19496"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0609.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0392","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0392.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0750","title":"Microsoft Hotmail 跨站脚本攻击漏洞","description":"Microsoft Hotmail 邮件服务在处理 HTML 格式邮件时未对 `<style>` 标签内的内容进行充分过滤，导致跨站脚本漏洞。远程攻击者可构造包含恶意 JavaScript 代码的邮件发送给受害者，当受害者使用浏览器（如 Internet Explorer 5、Netscape Communicator 4.0/4.5/4.6）查看邮件时，恶意脚本将在邮件上下文中自动执行，攻击者从而能够在受害者的 Hotmail 账户中执行任意操作，包括读取、发送、删除邮件以及修改账户设置。该漏洞利用方式简单，影响范围广泛，CVSS 评分 5.1，属于中等危害等级。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0750"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.727","remediation":"Microsoft 已在 1999 年的 Hotmail 服务端更新中修复此问题，用户升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 及以上版本可防止 STYLE 标签注入执行 JavaScript。Netscape Communicator 用户应升级至 4.7 及以上版本。当前 Hotmail 已迁移至 Outlook.com，使用最新版浏览器（Edge/Chrome/Firefox）和现代 Web 邮件服务可彻底规避此类攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/630","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19492"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0392.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0255","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0255.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0691","title":"多款 Unix 系统 CDE dtaction 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CDE 桌面环境 dtaction 工具中的 AddSuLog 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该函数传递超长的用户名字符串参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 DIGITAL UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 等多个 Unix 操作系统上的 CDE 2.1 版本，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地系统账号方能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0691"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.420","remediation":"对于 Solaris 7.0，安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 提供的补丁；AIX 4.3.2 安装 IBM APAR IY07482 补丁；HP-UX 应用 HPSBUX9909-103 公告补丁；Digital UNIX 4.0 安装 Compaq SSRT0746U 补丁；IRIX 6.5.14 安装 SGI 19990901-01-P 补丁。临措：移除 dtaction 的 setuid 位，`chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtaction`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/635","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A3078","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19497","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0691.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0691.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0691","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/a60c64eb75d37dbb82a1f2a085e4be6cfbbc462e/1999/CVE-1999-0691.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rq63-6647-rqxc/GHSA-rq63-6647-rqxc.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/ff974b2b48bc0a9f1df6a8c109ec03abf4db2138/1999/CVE-1999-0691.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0255.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0249","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0689","title":"Sun Solaris Common Desktop Environment dtspcd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Common Desktop Environment (CDE) 的 dtspcd 守护进程存在符号链接（symlink）漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接诱导 dtspcd 以提升的权限读取或写入任意文件，从而执行任意命令获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 CDE 2.1.20 及 Solaris 7.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0689"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.173","remediation":"安装 Sun 安全公告 #192 中对应平台的 dtspcd 补丁（Solaris 7：Patch ID 106594-01；Solaris 2.6：106593-01；Solaris 2.5.1：106592-01），HP-UX 用户安装 HPSBUX9909-103 补丁。临时缓解措施可停止 dtspcd 服务（/usr/dt/bin/dtspcd -kill）或移除其 setuid root 权限（chmod 555 /usr/dt/bin/dtspcd）。由于 CDE 已停止维护，建议迁移至 GNOME/KDE 等其他桌面环境作为根本解决方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/636","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1880","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19498","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0689","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0689.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c3dc2ea0-0265-4c0c-ae08-6be3c238c97a.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0450","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0450.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0751","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server Accept 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.51及3.6 SP2版本的Accept命令处理中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的Accept请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃或远程代码执行。受影响版本包括安装了SSL Handshake Patch的Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6，该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0751"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13","updated":"1999-09-13","remediation":"升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 3.6 SP3 或更高版本（3.6 SP2 及以下存在 Accept 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞）。由于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至现代 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx），并在迁移前通过防火墙限制对服务器 80/443 端口的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/631","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3256","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19493"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0450.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0246","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0246.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0687","title":"Sun Solaris ToolTalk ttsession 守护进程远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk ttsession 守护进程使用弱 RPC 认证机制（AUTH_UNIX），未启用更强的 AUTH_DES 认证，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞绕过认证直接执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.3~7.0 以及 HP-UX 等多种 Unix 操作系统版本，攻击者无需本地访问权限即可远程利用，导致系统完全受控。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0687"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.907","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 中提供的对应 Solaris 版本（2.3~7.0）补丁程序，或升级到已修复此问题的 Solaris 8 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 ttsession 服务行并重启 inetd 以禁用 ToolTalk 服务，同时在网络层面限制对 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）的访问。对于 HP-UX 系统，请参考 HP Security Bulletin HPSBUX9909-103 安装对应补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-001.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/637","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0246.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0309","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0702","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Import/Export Favorites 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0.1 及 5.x 版本的\"导入/导出收藏夹\"功能存在代码注入漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意收藏夹文件，诱使用户通过该功能导入，从而在用户系统上执行任意代码或修改文件。该漏洞影响 IE 4.0.1 至 5.01 版本，攻击者无需身份认证，利用难度低，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。Microsoft 已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0702"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.797","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 或更高版本以修复 ImportExportFavorites 漏洞。由于 IE 已停止支持，建议立即升级到 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器，并在组策略中禁用 ActiveX 控件和脚本执行作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ241361","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/627","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-037","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19490","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0702.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0702","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/da1ae45b8d49565b6ec43a0af3ddc2b6a2d9fdb0/1999/CVE-1999-0702/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0702.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0702.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2q7j-jrwg-8822/GHSA-2q7j-jrwg-8822.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0702.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0309.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0309.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0711","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0711.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0910","title":"Microsoft Site Server 和 MCIS Cookie 未设置过期时间漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 及商业 Internet 系统（MCIS）在生成会话 Cookie 时未设置过期时间，导致 Cookie 默认仅在浏览器会话期间有效，但可在会话结束后被重放利用。远程攻击者通过窃取或截获未设置过期时间的 Cookie，可冒充合法用户身份访问受保护的 Web 资源，导致会话劫持和信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 及 MCIS 系列产品。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0910"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-10","updated":"1999-09-10","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-035 提供的修补程序，该补丁修复了 Site Server/MCIS 在 Set-Cookie 响应中缺少过期头的问题。如无法立即更新，可配置代理服务器不缓存包含 Set-Cookie 头的页面，并关闭基于纯 Cookie 的身份验证机制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0711.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0273","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0273.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0697","title":"SCO Doctor 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO Doctor 管理工具中存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可通过该工具的 \"Tools\" 选项以 root 权限执行任意操作。攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限，利用该漏洞可完全控制受影响系统，包括修改系统配置、访问敏感数据及安装恶意程序。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户限制本地用户对 SCO Doctor 工具的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0697"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.187","remediation":"升级 SCO OpenServer 至 5.0.5 及以上版本，或安装 SCO 官方安全补丁 erg712103。如无法升级，移除 SCO Doctor 的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /opt/K/SCO/Doctor/1.0.0/bin/doctor），并限制可登录系统的本地用户账号数量，仅保留管理员可交互登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/621","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0697","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0697.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fwr5-hvj8-gff6/GHSA-fwr5-hvj8-gff6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6229833c-4cf2-4d79-b4d0-ced5f5ebb24d.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0273.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0482","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0767","title":"IBM AIX / Sun Solaris LC_MESSAGES 环境变量 libc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris libc 库、ufsrestore 及 rcp 工具在处理 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 4.2.1 及 Sun Solaris 7.0 等 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复该问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0767"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.953","remediation":"对 Sun Solaris 7.0 系统，安装 Sun 安全补丁 107733-01 或更新版本；对 IBM AIX 4.2.1 系统，升级到 APAR IX89537 修复版本或安装对应 bos.rte.libc 补丁包。无法立即升级时，可通过在 /etc/environment 或 shell 启动脚本中过滤 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量（如 unset LC_MESSAGES）来缓解该缓冲区溢出风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420557&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19217"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1309","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0926","title":"Apache HTTP Server MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及 1.3.1 版本在处理大量 MIME 头部时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含大量 MIME 头部的特制 HTTP 请求，可耗尽服务器资源致其崩溃，无法响应正常请求。该漏洞利用简单，攻击门槛低，受影响版本包括 Apache 1.2.5/1.3.1 及 UnityMail 2.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0926"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.597","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.3.2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法立即升级，可在 httpd.conf 中通过 `LimitRequestFields` 指令限制请求头字段数量，减小 MIME 头泛滥导致拒绝服务的攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1998_3/0742.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20272"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0725","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0725.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0925","title":"Messagemedia UnityMail 2.0 MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"MessageMedia UnityMail 2.0 邮件服务器在处理邮件 MIME 头部时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送包含大量 MIME 头的特制邮件，导致服务程序因资源耗尽而崩溃，影响正常邮件收发功能。该漏洞影响 UnityMail 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布相关安全公告。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0925"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.490","remediation":"建议升级至 UnityMail 2.1 或更高版本，该版本已在 MIME 解析器中加入头部数量限制。若供应商已停止支持该产品，应迁移至仍在维护的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exchange），并在边界邮件网关配置 MIME 头部数量阈值（建议≤100 个）作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90486243124867&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0725.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0244","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0244.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0685","title":"Netscape Communicator EMBED 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.06至4.61版本在处理EMBED标签的pluginspage选项时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意的HTML页面，诱导用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致浏览器崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响Netscape Communicator 4.x系列所有版本，攻击条件简单，用户仅需浏览恶意网页即可受影响。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0685"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-09-02","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"Netscape Communicator 已停止维护，建议立即停止使用该浏览器并迁移至现代浏览器（如 Firefox、Chrome、Edge）。如暂时无法迁移，请禁用浏览器插件功能并停止处理 untrusted 的 EMBED 标签内容。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/618","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19486","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0685"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0244.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0970","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1129","title":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 VLAN交换机 未授权VLAN遍历漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 系列虚拟局域网交换机中存在 IEEE 802.1q VLAN 遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造中继标签中的 VLAN 标识符，向其他 VLAN 注入 802.1q 帧，从而打破 VLAN 隔离机制实现跨 VLAN 访问。该漏洞允许攻击者无需认证即可绕过网络隔离策略，窃取或篡改不同 VLAN 中的敏感数据。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1129"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.940","remediation":"将所有非 trunk 端口设为静态 access 模式（`switchport mode access`），禁用 DTP（`switchport nonegotiate`），并在 trunk 端口上启用 VLAN 修剪（`vlan pruning`）以及限制允许的 VLAN 列表（`allowed vlan`）。同时配置本征 VLAN 为未使用的专用 ID 并关闭自动协商。这些措施可阻断伪造 802.1q 帧跨 VLAN 攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/univercd/cc/td/doc/product/lan/28201900/1928v8x/eescg8x/aleakyv.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/26008","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/615","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1129","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1129.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff02